description:
Minecraft survival. It is finally possible!! Today we revisit the EnderPorter teleportation system idea and redesign it from the ground up. Speed matters, so we also look into a new idea for high speed/long range redstone. 

Then we head to the Dual Blaze farm to finish up another one of our world's iconic builds.
